      <title>🚨🚨 Deadline extended! 🚨🚨 Submit your writing by November 30th for 𝒟𝑒𝓈𝒾𝑔𝓃 𝒜𝒻𝓉𝑒𝓇 𝒟...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DQeCQASiHL4/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DQeCQASiHL4/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/572814970_18422242840117474_5915021350473002857_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc1NTQ0OTAzNTE4OTE1NDU1Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=uXwJ56aLA7YQ7kNvwHW0rWe&amp;_nc_oc=Ado6cChyog5zKknBJv0h_NAUd0YANNARxOfGYQEGKoD16tdfez3RIcceTaqyR6YIVcE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=h-luGxunMPOmv_U3l-0HRg&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_AfxOFv-5XVM8-3-jARjoDwYITNcZ863q6paA9D2GKYkJLw&amp;oe=69CA3AE8" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @postfestival" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@postfestival</strong></p><p>🚨🚨 Deadline extended! 🚨🚨<br/>
<br/>
Submit your writing by November 30th for 𝒟𝑒𝓈𝒾𝑔𝓃 𝒜𝒻𝓉𝑒𝓇 𝒟𝑒𝓈𝒾𝑔𝓃: 𝒞𝓇𝒾𝓉𝒾𝒸𝒶𝓁 𝓌𝓇𝒾𝓉𝒾𝓃𝑔 𝒻𝑜𝓇 𝒶 𝒸𝒽𝒶𝓃𝑔𝒾𝓃𝑔 𝒹𝑒𝓈𝒾𝑔𝓃 𝓌𝑜𝓇𝓁𝒹.<br/>
<br/>
If you were hesitating – now is your chance!<br/>
<br/>
We have no concrete formats – essays, reflections, research-based deep-dives, speculative or experimental non-fiction – if it’s rigorous, bold, and thoughtful, we want to read it.<br/>
<br/>
Send us a max. 300 word proposal detailing your submission and a short bio. If you have previously published material, we would love to read it, so send us a link. <br/>
 <br/>
Contributors receive a fee of €350, we offer editorial support if needed and texts will then be published on our website and shared with the POST community internationally.<br/>
<br/>
📍 Deadline: November 30th <br/>
🔗 Read more on opencall.post.design<br/>
📬 Submit your proposal via our bio<br/>
<br/>
A collaborative project by : Post Design Festival (Copenhagen), Listya Amelia (Oslo) and Further Reading (Bandung)<br/>
<br/>
